{"tid":1385852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"網上轉載癱瘓狗鐵方法","createTime":"2019-07-30T07:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:44:14.000Z","uid":272922,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ebb625e8f215765b4557c11371b96ce690720c0e","tid":1385852,"uid":272922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:39:50.000Z","msg":"#網上轉貼<br />\n#千祈唔好學<br />\n<br />\n入實驗室撳緊急制？<br />\n<br />\n轉載：<br />\n真人真事。早兩日等地鐵，邊個站就唔好講，有條友，似乎係傻佬，㩒咗月台粒制，跟住走咗去。站長走去reset個制，搞咗幾分鐘，我口撩問佢，因為佢身材幾好。👨🏼&zwj;🔬=我，👷🏼&zwj;♀=站長）<br />\n<br />\n👨🏼&zwj;🔬：點解要reset?<br />\n👷🏼&zwj;♀：唔reset班車入唔到月台。<br />\n👨🏼&zwj;🔬︰咁麻煩，做乜要整咁多粒係人都㩒到嘅制喺個月台度？<br />\n👷🏼&zwj;♀：咁原意係如果乘客見到，或懷疑路軌上有雜物，有可能影響列車安全，就應該要㩒個制，等架車唔能夠入個站。<br />\n👨🏼&zwj;🔬︰咁你由得條友㩒完個制就咁走咗去？<br />\n👷🏼&zwj;♀：點捉佢？佢跑走咗啦。<br />\n👨🏼&zwj;🔬︰你月台有cctv㗎ma。<br />\n👷🏼&zwj;♀：冇用㗎，一頭一尾，中間影唔到（當時個傻佬就係喺月台中間㩒）。同埋捉到都冇用，正如我之前所講，基本上你懷疑路軌有雜物，就可以㩒，唔通公司用附例charge佢咩。就算charge到，都係罰1500蚊，冇阻嚇作用。<br />\n👨🏼&zwj;🔬︰如果幾個站都同時有人㩒咪好麻煩？<br />\n👷🏼&zwj;♀：係呀，基本上所有車都埋唔到站，癱瘓曬成條線，影響大過你拉車上個緊急制，不過正常冇咁橋嘅。其實公司最驚係咁。同埋如果個月台上幾粒制都俾人㩒咗，我要逐粒reset，就好麻煩。<br />\n👨🏼&zwj;🔬︰希望啲示威者唔好咁玩啦。<br />\n<br />\n講完之後，我就走出去追個傻佬啦。"},{"pid":"39d073e20ec14eff21c177bf2262cecb37c8fcf1","tid":1385852,"uid":272922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:40:36.000Z","msg":"有冇巴幫手fc個制係邊"},{"pid":"d96e8c57e8330726166e7d1ad144687336f33092","tid":1385852,"uid":1392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:41:01.000Z","msg":"夢想做工程師或者汽車維修員既同學仔入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383220</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫手推"},{"pid":"a17d82b934ae419009336380a6da0ac3604a1bc3","tid":1385852,"uid":272922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:41:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4e9b547e6e46f35f9979c996884aff638dcace5","tid":1385852,"uid":272922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90cc6c4a0db01367ce390ee515314d48e51e8ca3","tid":1385852,"uid":272922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:43:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dedab1249709461cb87c4873974ec9b1ecfcef30","tid":1385852,"uid":272922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:45:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5877a9ec255be5ceede419ec8b3cc06d36fee46c","tid":1385852,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bdc4f9728c661cc8d56f8d016f30f12bed52f40","tid":1385852,"uid":272922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:47:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d79b7a32068ebc9609b71dfdc071495fa9d0704","tid":1385852,"uid":272922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:51:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6602bbf25bc6ea4323cc818b489240f371133ff9","tid":1385852,"uid":272922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:44:14.000Z","msg":"推呀"}]}